org.apache.pirk.inputformat.hadoop

Class BaseInputFormat<Text,MapWritable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.mapreduce.InputFormat<Text,MapWritable>
      • org.apache.pirk.inputformat.hadoop.BaseInputFormat<Text,MapWritable>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    JSONInputFormatBase

    public abstract class BaseInputFormat<Text,MapWritable>
extends org.apache.hadoop.mapreduce.InputFormat<Text,MapWritable>
    All input formats used must extend this class

    MapWritable<K,V> should be of the form MapWritable<Text,Writable>

    If V is an array type, it must be of the form ArrayWritable
